I also do allot of city driving, and I keep it in 3rd gear to top out at
40mph, but usually throw it into 4th if I want to do a little
speeding.(which I usually do unless I am in heavy traffic.)  I run a
Non-Stock motor though, and can handle the higher rpms a bit better.

